        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4210784028" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer890718005502903137">I have to say I was intrigued by the synopsis for this book but wasn’t really sure if I would like it or not. It was a pleasant surprise that this turned out to be an entertaining and often humorous story, and one I’m glad I took a chance on. MacDonald isn’t an author I had come across before, but the entertaining way he wrapped an engaging plot, tight dialogue as well as good humour has made him an author I will definitely be looking out for in the future. This is without doubt quite a differen</span>
  <span id="freeText890718005502903137" style="display:none">I have to say I was intrigued by the synopsis for this book but wasn’t really sure if I would like it or not. It was a pleasant surprise that this turned out to be an entertaining and often humorous story, and one I’m glad I took a chance on. MacDonald isn’t an author I had come across before, but the entertaining way he wrapped an engaging plot, tight dialogue as well as good humour has made him an author I will definitely be looking out for in the future. This is without doubt quite a different book to most contemporary titles, but if you fancy something a little different I recommend giving it a go.</span>
  <a data-text-id="890718005502903137" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

